reviews.text: Nice place to relax when it is not that crowded. Good atmosphere and decor. Pretty expensive but the whole area is the same. You need to take an elevator up to the 2nd floor in order to reach the restaurant. I really liked the rice cake dish.

One of the most authentic Korean restaurant in Hong Kong. By far of all the authentic Korean restaurants in Hong Kong, this one is the best. Hands down. Their kimchijigeh is so authentic that it can contest with some of the best in Korea. 

Not only the food is good, the staff there are super nice too. And if you go with Koreans, they give 서비스 ;)

Highly recommend.

Always good food here. 5 stars

The wait, was insane. Booked at 830 or 9pm. Didn't get inside until 930. 
If do not know how to control tables leaving, then dont do 2 rounds dinner service. 

If you do 2 rounds dinner service. Then you better have ppl leave on time. Everyone waited over 30min and some eveb left. 

I will avoid coming on weekend
Cozy restaurant serving traditional Korean food.   Staff are friendly and food quality is good.  An excellent place for both casual dinner or intense soju drinking.
Great food! Great service!

reviews.text: 침사추이에 있는 한국 식당-텔포드 길에 있어서 처음 가보면 찾기가 쉽지는 않다. 그래도 늦게까지 영업을 하고 오뎅탕, 탕수육 이런 것들이 기본은 하는거 같다..가격은 뭐 홍콩에 있는 한국 식당처럼 비싸긴하다. 그래도 직원들, 사장님은 친절하다-

한국에서 편하게 술 한잔 마시는 듯한 분위기.
또한 가성비 좋은 회와 매운탕을 먹을 수 있는곳.

Nice place to relax when it is not that crowded. Good atmosphere and decor. Pretty expensive but the whole area is the same. You need to take an elevator up to the 2nd floor in order to reach the restaurant. I really liked the rice cake dish.
처음 가봤는데 음식이 정갈하고 맛있게 먹었음
好味，份量足。上餐有點慢，限時用餐有點太趕

reviews.text: Izzo makes amazing drinks!!!  I enjoy sitting at the bar and witness the process.  Beautiful!   Great for cocktail enthusiasts.
Good location at Knutsford, Food portion miserably small, mocktail are delicious and enjoyable comfortable sitting
Honestly this is the only bar that takes their time to perfect your drinks and is not stingy with their alcohol

One of the best spots in TST, with a surprisingly well stocked bar and very competent bar team. Nice music and good vibes, not too trashy like it's neighbors. Could do with some more interesting gins and some more attention to the bathroom's cleanliness on the weekends would also be advised but otherwise a great choice for a casual drink!
Best bar in Knutsford Terrace. Decent beer menu and food. Excellent decor too.
